Kafe
Kitchen / Defence

Mira
Anchoring - 1 - Place the Black Mirror facing Bakery and Red Hallway.
2 - Give callouts about enemies around bakary area.

Bandit
Anchoring - 1 - Place shock wire on Mira walls and fridge.
2 - Use the Black Mirror to cover the red hallway.

Maestro
Intel - Anchoring - 1 - Place Evil Eyes on bakery/Red hallway intersection and entrance lobby/fridge hallway intersection.
2 - Watch the Kitchen Main door t avoid Rush.

Jaeger
Roaming - 1 - Place ADS on bomb site and barbed wire at Kitchen main door.
2 - Cover the top floor along with Lesion to avoid vertical attack on the anchors. Wait for call and intel to rotate.

Lesion
Roaming - 1 - Place Gu Mines on bomb site entrances to avoid rush.
2 - Reinforce the fridge hatch and place Gu Mines on top floor to gain intel. Wait intel to roam.

