Kafe
3rd Floor / ATK

Thermite - 
Support - 1 Leave a Claymore and a Drone at the bottom of the back stairs. Use the Drone to give Intel to Nomad and Monty.
Step 2: Climb into the air conditioner and open the window to cover the top of the stairs and corridor between Bomb A and the smoking area. 
Provide cover and prevent rotation by this route.



Capitao
Support - 1 - Place a Claymore on the door leading to the balcony preventing peek from the reading room. Leave a drone in this area.
2 - Open the rappel pixel by the window, wait for call to throw smoke and fire during plant.



Gridlock
Support / Intel - 1 - Leave a drone in the smoking area/bar to get intel.
2 - Watch Bar/Bomb A Pixel, Smoke and Trap at Plant Time. After the Plant,
leave drones positioned to gain intel if you need to Rush towards the Defuser.



Nomad
Rush / Plant - 1 - Wait for Intel to Rush ladder, place an Airjab on the second half of ladder to prevent rotation.
2 - Reach the Bomb site A using Montagne's cover, plant the Defuser and position the remaining Airjabs around the Defuser.


Montagne
Rush / Cover - 1 - Wait for Support call to climb rear ladder. Before climbing the ladder position a Drone at its base for intel.
2 - Cover the rise of Nomad until the bomb. After the Plant covers the defuser with shield.

