Kafe
Reading Room / ATK


Thermite
Rush - 1 - Wait for Gridlock's call to jump from hatch in red stairs and take over Train area.
2 - Place a Claymore in the corridor that connects main hall and Bomb A corridor. After the plant, cover Gridlock's back on train.


Capitao
Support / Plant - 1 - Wait for Nomad's call to climb the back stairs with Montagne. Leave Claymore on the stairs to prevent rotation.
Use Smoke and Fire in the Reading room corridor to get to Bomb A and plant.



Gridlock
Support / Intel - 1 -Drone out to guide Thermite through the stairs and cover him in order to take over the train area.
2 - Wait for Capitao's arrival to throw Smoke and Trap at Bomb's door during plant.


Nomad
Support / Intel - 1 - Drone to guide  Montagne and Capitao through stairs. Put an Airjab at Respawn's door to avoid external peek while Rappelling.
2-After plant, open pixel on window and throw Airjab on door and fireplace.


Montagne
Rush / Cover - 1 - Wait for Support's call to climb the ladder. Before climbing the ladder position a Drone at its base for intel.
2 - Cover the path of the Capitao to bomb site. After the Plant Cover the Defuser.

